{
  "stem": "17135.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody has to be murdered anymore, because the victory is close, and the end is near.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and-- and it shook up even the SS.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The SS didn't know what to say, because they were used that people cry and beg for their lives.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was a-- they were so shocked that the commandant-- at that time, the commandant was [?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Schwartz, ?] was his name, a real murderer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He looked like a murderer this man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He started, [SPEAKING GERMAN], hang them-- screaming.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He-- he got mad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then they took one by one, and-- and-- and-- they didn't die fast enough.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were still pulling them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And everybody-- everybody was staring at this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then when they came to my brother, and they put the noose around him, he was again shouting, long live liberty!",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Long live liberty!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Anyway, all three were so courageous, and they really died like heroes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It had such a morale raising impact.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They really knew if people can live like this, and die like this, there is hope.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And let me tell you something, those three-- and then, after they were hanging there, they forced in single rows everybody to pass by to see this.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And-- and-- and people didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They were what we call a [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They-- they-- they-- they didn't know what to say in a sense.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "What-- those three people, while they were working, SS-- camp mason, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They had also a-- a room where they had all their-- their instruments and their-- their-- their work things and so, where they worked [? this. ?] They every night-- every night they at least fed 10 to 15 people.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They had access, because their work in the kitchen, the store.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They're organized.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
